{
  "sourceLanguage": "zh-Hans",
  "strings": {
    "·": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "shouldTranslate": false
    },
    "（未命名）": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Unnamed)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」是最后一台服务器。删除后将返回首次设置流程。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" is your last server. Deleting it returns you to first-run setup."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」是当前活动服务器。删除后将自动切换到列表中剩余的服务器。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" is the active server. Deleting it switches to another server in the list."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「允许完全访问」位于 设置 › 通用 › 键盘 › UniClip。系统未提供直达该页的链接,可从上方系统设置页逐级进入。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“Allow Full Access” lives in Settings › General › Keyboard › UniClip. iOS offers no direct link there — navigate from the Settings page above."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "%@": {},
    "%lld": {},
    "%lld 个": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%lld total"
          }
        }
      }
    },
