    "二维码内容损坏,请在桌面端重新生成。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "QR payload is corrupted. Re-generate it on the desktop."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "二维码声明的服务 \"%@\" 不是手机同步。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The QR's declared service \"%@\" is not mobile sync."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "二维码版本是 v%lld,本 App 暂不支持,请更新 App。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "QR uses protocol v%lld, which this app version doesn't recognize yet."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "二维码缺少必需字段 \"%@\",请在桌面端重新生成。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "QR is missing required field \"%@\". Re-generate it on the desktop."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "二维码里的服务地址不合法。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "QR contains an invalid server URL."
