    "从 ${server} 接收": {},
    "从 UniClipboard 服务器拉取最新内容并作为快捷指令的输出返回;默认同时写入本机剪贴板。可指定来源服务器。": {},
    "从 UniClipboard 服务器拉取最新的剪贴板内容,写入到本机剪贴板。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pull the latest clipboard content from your UniClipboard server and write it to this device's clipboard."
          }
        }
