    "触感反馈": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Haptic Feedback"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "在 UniClip 键盘上点按时的声音与振动。按键音还受系统「设置 › 声音与触感」里「键盘点击音」总开关影响;触感反馈需要键盘「允许完全访问」。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sound and vibration when you tap keys on the UniClip keyboard. Key clicks also depend on the system “Keyboard Clicks” switch in Settings › Sounds & Haptics; haptic feedback requires Full Access for the keyboard."
          }
        }
      }
    },
