    "关闭": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Close"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "关闭（推荐）：在主页用「粘贴」按钮一键推送，iOS 不会弹窗。开启后会自动读取并推送本机复制的内容——iOS 在读取其他 App 复制的内容时会弹出「允许粘贴」确认。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Off (recommended): push with one tap of the Paste button on the home screen — iOS shows no prompt. When on, content you copy is read and pushed automatically; iOS shows an \"Allow Paste\" confirmation each time it reads content copied from another app."
          }
        }
      }
    },
