    "在 设置 › 通用 › 键盘 › UniClip 中开启「允许完全访问」,即可在打开键盘时自动同步剪贴板。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Turn on “Allow Full Access” in Settings › General › Keyboard › UniClip to auto-sync your clipboard whenever the keyboard opens."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "在任意输入框切换到 UniClip 键盘时,会把本机刚复制的文本或图片自动发送到当前服务器,并把服务器最新的内容作为候选,点一下即可直接插入——全程不经过系统剪贴板,不会反复弹「允许粘贴」。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Switch to the UniClip keyboard in any text field and it sends the text or image you just copied to the current server, then offers the server's latest content as a candidate you can insert with one tap — all without touching the system pasteboard or repeatedly prompting “Allow Paste”."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "在系统设置中开启「位置」权限以读取当前 WiFi": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
