    "点按后 iOS 会弹出一次「允许粘贴」。允许后,主程序也能在「自动推送本机剪贴板」开启时静默读取并推送,并会在 设置 › UniClip 出现「粘贴自其他 App」开关。授权按 App 独立,键盘会在首次使用时单独询问。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tapping it prompts “Allow Paste” once. After you allow it, the main app can also read and push silently when “Auto-push device clipboard” is on, and a “Paste from Other Apps” switch appears under Settings › UniClip. Authorization is per app — the keyboard asks separately on first use."
          }
        }
      }
